query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(ci it1 mi n t mi_idx) NoNestLoop(ci it1 mi mi_idx n t it2) */ select min(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
min(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
min(t.title) AS movie_title
from name AS n
inner join cast_info AS ci
on n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'm' AND n.name like '%Jones,%' AND ci.note IN ('(uncredited)',
'(executive producer)')
inner join title AS t
on t.id = ci.movie_id
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id
inner join info_type AS it1
on it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'budget'
inner join movie_info_idx AS mi_idx
on t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
inner join info_type AS it2
on it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'votes';
